{"tid":1825773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有份聯署就嚟截止，仲差五萬幾人呀","createTime":"2020-01-15T14:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T13:00:22.000Z","uid":260093,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f392e14ffbe202a40bdd2cae80eb310b25dd8545","tid":1825773,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"差5萬3千，截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\">17/1/2020</span><br />\n聯邦政府應將習近平的女兒從美國驅逐出境<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Ffederal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=a7a83b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其餘13個聯署，更新日9/1/2020<br />\n<br />\n欠34萬8千，要100萬先達標，大家努力簽署🙏💪<br />\n(1)要求常設仲裁法院調查香港警察的非法武力<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/CmMgwSyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FCmMgwSyM&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=c2064cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/CmMgwSyM</a><br />\n<br />\n欠83萬8千，要100萬先達標，大家努力簽署🙏💪<br />\n(2) 呼籲日本議員開始討論《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XI1gv1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XI1gv1&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b7842cf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XI1gv1</a><br />\n<br />\n(3)投訴江永祥失實言論及游乃強調職安排<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ucxzprNYjvjSAcSC6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FucxzprNYjvjSAcSC6&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b0202acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ucxzprNYjvjSAcSC6</a><br />\n<br />\n欠89萬1千，要100萬先達標，大家努力簽署🙏💪<br />\n(4)取消楊潤雄的家庭成員的澳大利亞國籍<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/6YpF26cw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2F6YpF26cw&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=fd6b19a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/6YpF26cw</a><br />\n<br />\n(5)譴責警方於崇光百貨一帶無差別拘捕市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSebX9rMIw87wb2uXYuuggtAhbHkyge5BlHfj5HcLyUFOMv-zg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSebX9rMIw87wb2uXYuuggtAhbHkyge5BlHfj5HcLyUFOMv-zg%2Fviewform&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=fb549b56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSebX9rMIw87wb2uXYuuggtAhbHkyge5BlHfj5HcLyUFOMv-zg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\nNEW 欠93萬3千，要100萬先達標，努力簽署💪🙏<br />\n(6)授權英國廢除《中英加入宣言》。恢復她對香港的管轄權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-parliament-authorise-uk-to-abolish-sino-british-join-declaration-reinstate-her-jurisdiction-to-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-parliament-authorise-uk-to-abolish-sino-british-join-declaration-reinstate-her-jurisdiction-to-hk&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=d613492a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-parliament-authorise-uk-to-abolish-sino-british-join-declaration-reinstate-her-jurisdiction-to-hk</a><br />\n<br />\nNEW 欠9萬5千，截止日期2/2/2020一<br />\n(7)作為中美第二階段協議的一部分，呼籲在香港增加真正的雙重普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=34bf9f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n<br />\nNEW 差9萬5千，截止日期2/2/2020<br />\n(8)《香港人權與民主法》是時候進行評估了<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=0fd7377d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation</a><br />\n<br />\n差8萬7千，截止日期1/2/2020<br />\n(9)香港普選計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=86a8d82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n差8萬4千，截止日期28/1/2020<br />\n(10)對香港警察和官員及其直系親屬施加旅行禁令<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-travel-ban-hong-kong-police-officer-hksar-government-officials-their-immediate-family-usa-allies-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fimpose-travel-ban-hong-kong-police-officer-hksar-government-officials-their-immediate-family-usa-allies-1&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=53ed4a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-travel-ban-hong-kong-police-officer-hksar-government-officials-their-immediate-family-usa-allies-1</a><br />\n<br />\n差6萬3，截止日期27/1/2020<br />\n(11)北京2022年冬奧會企業贊助商不應享有稅收優惠<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e5beac49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a><br />\n<br />\n差9萬，截止日期24/1/2020<br />\n(12)禁止匯豐銀行進入美國金融系統，以協助其處理各種侵犯人權行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/ban-hsbc-its-access-us-financial-system-assistance-various-human-right-abuse-behaviors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fban-hsbc-its-access-us-financial-system-assistance-various-human-right-abuse-behaviors&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e234f384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/ban-hsbc-its-access-us-financial-system-assistance-various-human-right-abuse-behaviors</a><br />\n<br />\n差5萬6千，截止日期24/1/2020<br />\n(13)要求關閉&ldquo;香港警方&rdquo;的facebook帳戶<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/demand-close-down-facebook-account-hong-kong-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fdemand-close-down-facebook-account-hong-kong-police&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4ee4f8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/demand-close-down-facebook-account-hong-kong-police</a>"},{"pid":"ac70712dd8050fc67f2d33c75625f8cd8882dadd","tid":1825773,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點會唔夠人架，歹劣人冇理由唔想老甴個女番歸</span>"},{"pid":"efff819563da69e04396c8e69b528eb52c3ad703","tid":